Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:13.66,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,カラダはこんなにクタクタに疲れてるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:24.32,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ココロはどうしてドキドキが止まらないんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:30.35,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,昨日とちがう明日があること
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:38.29,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,信じられる自分がいるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.72,0:01:40.83,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,今日も走れ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:47.09,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,倒れたって恥ずかしくない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:51.33,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,もう一度立ち上がれば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.91,0:01:57.71,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,あと少しでたどり着けそうな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:02:01.64,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,予感がしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:07.02,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,夢の地図なんていらない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:12.73,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,目指す場所はもうずっと決まっている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.22,0:02:21.30,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,新しい世界にいま出会いたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:13.66,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,明明身体这么疲惫不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:24.32,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么却抑制不住内心的激动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:30.35,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,和昨天不同 明天是新的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:38.29,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如果相信自己的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.72,0:01:40.83,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也迈开大步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:47.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,就算被打倒也不觉得丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:51.33,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,再次站起来就行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.91,0:01:57.71,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点就能抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:02:01.64,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我有这种预感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:07.02,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不需要什么梦幻地图
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:12.73,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我的目标早已决定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.22,0:02:21.30,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,好想立刻邂逅全新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:22:03.24,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ボクの見ていた　一人分の景色の中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:09.24,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,君の色があたりまえになる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.63,0:22:13.46,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,知らなかった心地いい距離や
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.88,0:22:17.18,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,くだらない意地の張り合い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:21.89,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ほらまたすぐに笑い合えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.21,0:22:28.92,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,日常を重ね合って行く　途切れず強くなって行く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:37.11,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ボクの心はきっと君の半分が満たすんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.37,0:22:38.74,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ぴったりと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.21,0:22:43.20,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,もっと寄り添って生きて行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.66,0:22:46.79,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ボク等なんだか似てるね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:53.37,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,頼りないとこも 補ってちょうどいいとこも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:57.57,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ちゃんと向き合って生きて行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.94,0:23:00.59,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,偶然の引力は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:10.20,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,神様だって予測できない必然示してるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:22:03.24,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我所看到的 一人份的景色中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:09.24,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你的颜色 渐渐变得司空见惯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.63,0:22:13.46,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,进入从未体验过的惬意距离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.88,0:22:17.18,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,无聊的赌气之后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:21.89,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,看 马上又笑在一块了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.21,0:22:28.92,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的日常渐渐重合 不断变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:37.11,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,有你作“半”一定能填补我心中的空洞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.37,0:22:38.74,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如此的契合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.21,0:22:43.20,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,再更靠近一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.66,0:22:46.79,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我们好像很相似呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:53.37,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不可靠的地方也都能互相弥补
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:57.57,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,好好面对彼此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.94,0:23:00.59,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,偶然的引力谕示着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:10.20,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,连神明都无法预测的必然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.25,0:00:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.71,0:00:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是地下城对我们的憎恶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.63,0:00:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它把藏身于此的我们视为眼中钉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乌拉诺斯 你的祈祷哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没听说会发生这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是阶层主么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:27.90,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1100,164)}{\fad(450,450)}眷族的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:27.90,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1100,104)}{\fad(450,450)}Familiar Myth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.11,0:02:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶紧去救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.73,0:02:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的打算用这只队伍去救他们么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去救他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个不合格的队长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你并没有做错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.76,0:03:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千草小姐 上神大人就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.57,0:03:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 千万不要勉强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没戏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咆..咆哮？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 为什么..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会变这样..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你会妨碍到贝尔大人 所以把你拖走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好感谢我们家那位来者不拒的老好人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去把能找到的武器和冒险者全都找来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要讨伐阶层主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了 安朵美达
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不是一般的阶层主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退路已经被切断了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上 我们已不可能离开这个阶层了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非打倒那个家伙 不然就无法逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:05:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小的们 准备和那个怪物大干一场吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把镇上的家伙全都给我赶出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些畏缩怕事灭自家威风的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将永远不准再踏入这个镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让大家看看咱们冒险者的骨气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快离开那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无形鬼火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:05:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然和通常的阶层主不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜在能力到达了等级5
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利昂 援军到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在起 镇上的魔导师们将开始进行咏唱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你继续吸引歌利亚的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起分散敌人的注意力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞 小的们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安朵美达将亲自担当诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就放心大胆地开始咏唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给它来一发大的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯斯 这笔帐我记下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,争取时间 只要撑到咏唱结束..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然厉害..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器多得是 坏了就赶紧换一把
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就是临时拼凑的队伍 就别管什么配合了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不彼此妨碍就行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按各自的性子去战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 前锋后撤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要送它一份大礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我狠狠地打！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气干掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自我再生..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克朗尼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请克朗尼先生挡住周围的怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我们去压制歌利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让它继续肆虐下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:09:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要争取到时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚有战力的魔导师就能施放出下一轮魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这样还不管用 就一轮接一轮..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到打倒它为止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫斯缇雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支援者小姐 你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请把能找到的装备都搜集过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了吧 拜托你回镇上一趟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千草大人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到刚才的爆炸她就跑出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是去樱花他们那边了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利昂 你这样会死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.54,0:11:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也必须做我该做的才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙太硬了 想攻击魔石也无从下手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去迟早..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便这样..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要还有希望..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.48,0:11:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千草 拿盾来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 会死的..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱花会死的..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你 千草
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想成为只会嘴上说说的卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想成为眼看他人牺牲而无动于衷的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克朗尼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利昂 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰闪电
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.37,0:13:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱花大人 樱花大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱花..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.53,0:13:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克朗尼先生 请回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔 他的情况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有呼吸..不过伤口很深
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利昂 这里交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千草小姐 之后就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去吧 精灵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽可能多争取一些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔绝对会醒过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会醒过来 打倒那个怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女神赫斯缇雅..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也见识过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔的话一定能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔的话一定能打倒那个怪兽的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔 醒一醒啊贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在战斗 面对那么可怕的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.70,0:14:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能拯救大家的只有你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来 贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔 贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上神大人 我明白的 我听见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.04,0:14:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 身体却怎么都..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体怎么都动弹不得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动啊 动啊 快动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须去战斗 为了上神大人为了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有资格被称为英雄的..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既不是仗剑之人 也不是举盾之人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更不是疗伤止痛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能赌上自己性命的人 才能被称为英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.89,0:15:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护同伴拯救红颜  赌上自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遭遇挫折也没关系 备受打击也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情哭泣吧 胜者永远存在于败者之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贯彻你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喊出你的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是最帅气的男子汉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不愧对那个人..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更为了拯救重要的同伴们..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔大人..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你 贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃烧憧憬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喊出愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界限解除？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.16,0:16:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让它们过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻幽远森林的上空..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无限繁星点缀无穷夜天..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回应我愚钝的请求..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再度赐下星火之加护..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以光之慈悲宽恕弃汝而去之人..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种高速战斗中同时进行咏唱？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然这么高..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨口拙舌 诚惶诚恐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战无不胜的吾之武神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无上尊天的指引啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请赋予卑小之身以巍然御体之神力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我这么说很自私
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我真的需要帮助一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 让我粉碎你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流离之冽风..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流浪之旅人..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,横跨苍穹穿越荒野..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我也得拿出看家本领了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,携星屑之芒以御敌..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光明之风
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:48.53,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Luminos Wind
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自天降临 一统大地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神武斗征 布都御魂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重力的结界..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顶不住了..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.41,0:18:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火月！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 克罗佐的魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然超越了原型？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要把执念和同伴放在天平上比较
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 那只是执念而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对不讲理的压倒性力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅凭一股微不足道的力量实现逆转
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄的一击！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:19:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连那一击也..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的贝尔·克朗尼..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他能够更快..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更强..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更高地飞跃！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔大人 贝尔大人成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:20:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一手嘛 小小新秀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.14,0:21:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我荷米斯确实见识到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无资质？别说傻话了 宙斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的孙子 你的临别赠礼是货真价实的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.45,0:21:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是你的眷族留下的最后的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转动了 时代要向前转动了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会亲眼见证
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将发生在这里 这块欧拉丽大地的..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,载入史册的大事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄们的兴衰荣辱 他们的生与死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的他们所编织的 眷族的故事..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.69,0:21:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Familiar Myth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.58,0:22:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,角度很刁钻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.75,0:22:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以发生了那种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.96,0:22:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在喝着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.22,0:22:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很努力呢
